~ FrontEnd consists of components and screens
  Initially when you create a react app we have index.js and its related files in our src folder
  This acts as entry point to app, it contains all the CSS related file import and we place <App /> here which in term calls out App.js file which we create
  App.js contains our main App- Routes andbasic structure of components like Header-Screens-Footer various components of our application called.
  'react-router-dom' - Link useParams
  We have used 'react-bootstrap' which gives various bootstrap ui related functionalities build in like containers,cards,rows,cols etc etc
  useState,useEffect
  axios
  
~ Backend
  Created Server.js file which contains express app with get requests - sending product information from ./data/products.js
